            "title": "A股早段向下   深股跌0.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股早市低開後跌幅擴大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指開報3358點，跌5點或0.15%，現報3355點，跌7點或0.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指開報10091點，跌36點或0.36%，現報10077，跌48點或0.48%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報3850黜，跌8點或0.21%，現報3851，跌7點或0.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數開報2002點，跌10點或0.5%，現報2000點，跌12點或0.61%。</p>\n</div>",
